  <brief_title>The Outcome After Lichtenstein Operation vs. ProGrip Patch Repair of Inguinal Hernia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Mesh Type on Pain After Surgery for Inguinal Hernia. Randomized Clinical Trial of Lichtenstein Operation With Sutured Polypropylene Patch or Self-adhesive ProGrip Patch.</official_title>
